f7\"> 하오니,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-646665e3-07fd-4e59-ae82-b2830f6a0cfe\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5abc14d9-1945-4cc7-9021-89e1a10af89d\">이 점 참고해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-634865b0-fa21-42cf-94b6-b0791fdd742c\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9b99e674-ac72-4c9d-ba3d-73d66be36399\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-d6ba51f7-4b12-49fd-a403-29c78a175bf6\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-6f15441b-81a0-4280-94d3-685b41ebe705\"><b>5월 1일(월) 근로자의날</b></span><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2a492d85-326c-48c1-8084-04bc7c68758c\">과 </span><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-6c0d76c8-47d1-4824-b05b-968e36e81574\"><b>5월 29일(월) 석가탄신일</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-9dfd99b6-8424-4265-b2a7-8865da5edcfa\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-bd3ca929-c50a-4ee3-9991-dbf3239b4a28\">대체공휴일에는 </span><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1db79a95-a32d-4e99-bac8-b71cdce0ee1d\"><b>정상진료</b></span><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-77e974c9-57f7-4b9d-b5b8-e4b76d21a76c\">를 진행할 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-92857a43-3711-4593-8164-c15944bf6893\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c1e67fec-0824-4cc5-8f41-f6d53cb170e6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-c6eee2cf-2a63-4465-9f53-2559c1a36775\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-02608b83-b419-47ff-bb3a-6359a3036822\">예약하시는 분들은 이 점 참고하시어 내원해 주시기를 부탁드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-e457ec52-71a7-402c-b65d-f607b270934a\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0705cf55-9842-40f6-9cd8-6ef68b3d3138\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-d88b48d5-efb2-494a-b4ec-051dea6bc412\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-67b2d49a-a0de-472f-9c94-105297cb10da\">우리 병원은 항상 환자분들의 건강과 행복을 최우선으로 생각하며,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-90d4e88d-8413-4869-80ad-a052d00304f2\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3c8b48b5-5c39-4860-8b97-3f2bc0ac4690\">최상의 진료와 서비스를 제공하기 위해 노력하는 이수한의원이 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-bc8fda81-64cf-4ddf-8f1f-1173e76170f5\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-684a23e3-64cb-4ba0-b360-66f9182db731\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-db03d9d0-1b7a-44f4-b007-9a0fcd697719\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-fb19d12c-afd1-49f7-a6cc-fabe29444d69\">언제나 환자분들이 편하게 내원하실 수 있도록 최선을 다하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-6068b351-162e-4e5a-9b50-387d10c3c4d5\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f96dd09d-fb9f-4db6-a8c0-9e6cf05dac8e\">궁금한점이 있으면 톡톡으로 문의주세요. 감사합니다 :)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-6ea09bb1-5a86-43e1-b851-76dca09049fc\"><span style=\"color:#374151;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-054bf56a-e60c-49d7-94aa-f03905dff44c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-ea3c51df-80f4-4e44-93f4-90cfc5cbf64e\"><span style=\"color:#374151;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1e7ec50c-77af-4387-a6b9-5df2f50d4512\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n          